tool_description:
Generate quirky names for your project/app/server. e.g. vivacious-flood, divine-rooster-7539
Generate unique, pronunciable strings
name: Project Name Generator
title: Project Name Generator

api_list.name: Without Number
api_list.description: Get a project name without a number. e.g. diligent-teddy
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://acedev-project-name-generator-v1.p.rapidapi.com/without-number"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "acedev-project-name-generator-v1.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
